data.description: OFFER DEADLINE 11/26    Welcome to this charming ranch-style home nestled in the heart of Capitol Heights, Maryland. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this residence offers an inviting and comfortable living space for your family. The well-maintained property features a spacious interior with a cozy, open floor plan, perfect for hosting gatherings or simply enjoying daily life. A standout feature of this home is the generously sized lot of land located behind the property, providing ample space for outdoor activities, gardening, or potential expansion. In addition to the home's fantastic features, its prime location is a true highlight, with the Addison-Road Seat Pleasant Metro station just a short walk away. This convenient proximity to public transportation ensures easy access to the greater Washington, D.C. area. Furthermore, the neighborhood offers a range of amenities including nearby dining options, gas stations, parks, and more, making it an ideal place to call home.  This ranch-style residence not only offers comfortable living but also the convenience of urban amenities and serene surroundings. The well-designed layout and the spacious lot provide endless possibilities for both indoor and outdoor activities. With excellent access to transportation, dining, and recreational opportunities, this home in Capitol Heights presents an enticing opportunity for those looking to enjoy the best of suburban living within close reach of the city. Don't miss the chance to make this lovely property your own and experience the harmonious blend of comfort, convenience, and nature in this desirable Maryland location.
